text: Wolfgard Voss (, Mönning, 24 June 1926 - 7 July 2020), nicknamed "Wölfi", was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1926 births Category:2020 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Oldenburg (city)
